metadata.name: Prima Materia
metadata.description: The Prima Materia is the most fundamental substance of alchemy, the raw material from which all things are made. It is the starting point of the Magnum Opus, the Great Work, and the key to unlocking the secrets of the universe. It is a rare and elusive essence, the Dew of the Ã†ther, and the subject of much lore and speculation among those who delve into the arcane arts.
